<p>Issues</p>
<ol>
<li>De-urbanisation of industry - shifting to rural areas + low human n physical infrastructure</li>
<li>Absorb agro labour - skill,&nbsp;</li></ol>
<p>Potential&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>Rural distress - more jobs needed , also agro productivity improvement , both can benefit from SME&nbsp;</li>
<li>Rural urban green growth difference - urban areas more energy efficient.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<li>Land is asset in rural areas.&nbsp;</li></ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>way forward&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>Structural transformation of rural - agro productivity + jobs +women opportunity&nbsp;</li>
<li>VGF , e.g. DoNER gave such for medicinal plants in NER&nbsp;</li></ol>
